  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>The Cosmos Needs Hunters. Are You Up for the Challenge?</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An alien scourge ravages the cosmos. You are a HUNTER, the galaxy’s elite defense. Deploy in this top-down roguelite arena shooter and take the fight to the enemy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter small, fast-paced arenas where you must eliminate all enemies. Engage in quick, action-packed missions, experiment with powerful abilities and augments, and unlock unique cosmetics to customize your appearance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The system’s last hope rests on your trigger finger. Will you rise to the challenge?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837680/extras/060b6796cb6a3e49ed59427afda599e5.poster.avif?t=1740756662\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837680/extras/060b6796cb6a3e49ed59427afda599e5.webm?t=1740756662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837680/extras/060b6796cb6a3e49ed59427afda599e5.mp4?t=1740756662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunt down every enemy in short but challenging encounters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837680/extras/2e8943dc30606d6e11fb07815fc0f26a.poster.avif?t=1740756662\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837680/extras/2e8943dc30606d6e11fb07815fc0f26a.webm?t=1740756662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837680/extras/2e8943dc30606d6e11fb07815fc0f26a.mp4?t=1740756662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experiment with a variety of skills and upgrades to suit your playstyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837680/extras/ad73e57ee4996dac283ee61224bfebe3.poster.avif?t=1740756662\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837680/extras/ad73e57ee4996dac283ee61224bfebe3.webm?t=1740756662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837680/extras/ad73e57ee4996dac283ee61224bfebe3.mp4?t=1740756662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Harvest crystals across diverse planets to unlock permanent upgrades and cosmetics. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Good luck, Hunter.</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>The Cosmos Needs Hunters. Are You Up for the Challenge?</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An alien scourge ravages the cosmos. You are a HUNTER, the galaxy’s elite defense. Deploy in this top-down roguelite arena shooter and take the fight to the enemy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter small, fast-paced arenas where you must eliminate all enemies. Engage in quick, action-packed missions, experiment with powerful abilities and augments, and unlock unique cosmetics to customize your appearance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The system’s last hope rests on your trigger finger. Will you rise to the challenge?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837680/extras/060b6796cb6a3e49ed59427afda599e5.poster.avif?t=1740756662\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837680/extras/060b6796cb6a3e49ed59427afda599e5.webm?t=1740756662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837680/extras/060b6796cb6a3e49ed59427afda599e5.mp4?t=1740756662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunt down every enemy in short but challenging encounters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837680/extras/2e8943dc30606d6e11fb07815fc0f26a.poster.avif?t=1740756662\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837680/extras/2e8943dc30606d6e11fb07815fc0f26a.webm?t=1740756662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837680/extras/2e8943dc30606d6e11fb07815fc0f26a.mp4?t=1740756662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experiment with a variety of skills and upgrades to suit your playstyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837680/extras/ad73e57ee4996dac283ee61224bfebe3.poster.avif?t=1740756662\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837680/extras/ad73e57ee4996dac283ee61224bfebe3.webm?t=1740756662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837680/extras/ad73e57ee4996dac283ee61224bfebe3.mp4?t=1740756662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Harvest crystals across diverse planets to unlock permanent upgrades and cosmetics. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Good luck, Hunter.</i></p>",
